{"tid":2427722,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"嚴防220入獄民主派人士監獄暴動， 港官員 : 黑豹部隊隨時空降平亂","createTime":"2021-03-01T04:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T05:33:55.000Z","uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f139c8c603f9dd8f0c7109264386a0dbe9cae8a1","tid":2427722,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:04:56.000Z","msg":"自香港國安法於2020年6月實施以來，短短不到1年，便有大批「反修例」示威者遭當局檢控清算，陸續進入監獄還押、服刑，擴及當地青年、甚至議員等人士。對此，香港懲教署署長胡英明稱懲教署早早部署，特別加強俗稱的「黑豹部隊」，<strong>配有實彈槍械及武器用以迅速平亂。</strong><br />\n<br />\n胡英明受訪時表示，截至今 (22) 日約有超過220名相關人士，因涉國安法遭還押、定罪、保釋候審等而出入懲教院所，警方稍早更稱已檢控逾2000人，預計進入懲教院所的人數只會陸續增加。<br />\n<br />\n胡英明直言，<strong>根據過去經驗，若背景和理念相同的人聚集，便會出現對抗管方等衝突，</strong>為此署方便須防患未然，<strong><span class=\"red\">將相同背景人士「打散」安排於不同懲教院所，</span></strong>並視個別影響力及犯罪嚴重性，入住不同保全級別的懲教院所；另外，也會部署配有實彈槍械及低殺傷力武器的「黑豹部隊」，並與港府飛行服務隊合作，一旦發生突發事故，人員可在一小時內空降至各院所平亂，分別已於去年和前年出動過335及444次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-02-22/539561\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2021-02-22%2F539561&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3ajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=0b4768f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2021-02-22/539561</a>"},{"pid":"3abfb9cf2f69cc6cac1e1986845ca18010580cbf","tid":2427722,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:09:43.000Z","msg":"懲教短命種聯乘飛曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7b4ad66a2de8dc5622a55f8a64510554525fe7","tid":2427722,"uid":85629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T04:13:59.000Z","msg":"唔講以為係南美洲嗰啲監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以要有實彈配備<br />\n<br />\n不過都係得個名嚇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔通你真係開實彈咩"},{"pid":"021f500a350bedf7e8363c9d3b1c3b8a9a33fbd9","tid":2427722,"uid":216664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T05:33:55.000Z","msg":"快follow香港流亡議會<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkshadowparliament.com/zh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkshadowparliament.com%2Fzh%2F&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3ajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=ca035340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkshadowparliament.com/zh/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHkbhnY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHkbhnY.png&h=175cef92&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}